headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Bonuses on Acid Lab Sell and Resupply Missions
content:
It’s time to ramp up production to meet the high demand in the increasingly trippy Los Santos drug scene. Whether you’re running home deliveries, dodging police ambushes, or going stealth mode, the goal in Acid Lab Sell Missions stays the same: drop off product, avoid getting caught, and earn 1.5X GTA$ and RP all week long.

Speaking of illicit economics, make sure production keeps up with demand. Help Mutt stay stocked by engaging in Acid Lab Resupply Missions this week to earn Double Supplies.
